terms.medium_def:
A man from the tribe of Levi living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at 1Ch.9.19; 
only referred to as Kore (קוֹרֵא); 
son of Ebiasaph; 
a brother of Assir.

A man living at the time of Divided Monarchy, only mentioned at 2Ch.31.14; 
only referred to as Kore (קוֹרֵא); 
a son of Imnah.
